{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: M.C.S. JACK over WENDY.
{META_DATA}: 48.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{DIALOGUE}: I fell in love with it right away.
{DIALOGUE}: When I came up here from my interview, it was as though I had been here before.
{DIALOGUE}: We...we all have moments of deja vu, but this was ridiculous.
{DIALOGUE}: It was almost as though I knew what was going to be around every corner.
