{META_DATA}: (on T.V.)
{DIALOGUE}: Good evening.
{DIALOGUE}: I'm Glen Rinker Newswatch 10.
{DIALOGUE}: While Miami continues to swelter in a record winter heatwave bringing temperatures to the mid and upper nineties, the Central and Rocky Mountain States are buried in snow.
{META_DATA}: (MORE)
{META_DATA}: 77.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GLEN RINKER (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: In Colorado ten inches of snow has fallen in just a few hours tonight.
{DIALOGUE}: Travel in the Rockies is almost impossible.
