{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. HOTEL - GOLD BALLROOM - M.L.S.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Entrance to Gold Ballroom - CAMERA TRACKS FORWARD through entrance to photographs on wall.
