{META_DATA}: DISSOLVE TO:
{META_DATA}: 147.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: M.S. Photograph of Guests at Ball.
{META_DATA}: DISSOLVE TO:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: M.C.S. Photograph of YOUNG MAN in dinner jacket.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CAMERA TILTS DOWN TO:
{META_DATA}: OVERLOOK HOTEL JULY 4th BALL 1921
{META_DATA}: FADE OUT.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: BLACK FRAMES.
